GoldenEye:
She looked at Destructor. "Yes, I was with KitKat a long time ago, 
then we became separated. I am here to return to her group."  She 
looked up."Just out of curousity, is this bot flying around the base 
one of your's?"

DarkMouse::
She walked up to the other two. "Hey Destructor. This bot over here 
is trying to attack the base. And KitKat went to go meet Megatron in 
the clearing."
